    "Relevant information could not get from TAL scale; however, SUS gave meaningful results.3.3.5.",
    "Basic Home Activities: SUS was used as an evaluation tool for the study targeting basic home activities [100] via smart phone applications.3.3.6.",
    "Food Related Activities: Food related activities were evaluated with open-ended interview by van Doornvan Atten et al. [77] and Technology Usage Inventory (TUI) by Perotti and Strutz, 2023 [131].",
